RED ROIDS
A simple 2D vector space shooter

To build on Ubuntu 11.10:
sudo apt-get install build-essential libsdl-gfx1.2-dev
./compile.sh

Key       Action
=====================================================
ESC   BACKSPACE         Exits (First to Main menu, then completely)
F1                      Loops through debug modes
W     I       UP        Burn thrusters
A     J       LEFT      Rotate counter clockwise
D     L       RIGHT     Rotate clockwise
Q     SPACE   SHIFT     Fire blasters
T             NUMPAD_0  Find better target
Z                       Toggle zoom view
N                       Switch ship

